Introduction
Welcome to FuelCompare's Privacy Policy. Your privacy is crucial to us. This policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and safeguarding of your personal information in compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). FuelCompare operates through both our website and mobile applications for iOS and Android. FuelCompare is operated by FuelcompareIreland, and can be contacted at info@fuelcompare.ie.
Your Consent
By using our website or mobile apps, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of this policy, please do not use our website or mobile apps.
Note: You can withdraw your consent at any time by contacting us or deleting your account.
Information We Collect
Personal Information
Name and email for account creation
Location data for nearby stations
Device information for notifications
Usage Information
Browser type and version
Usage statistics and patterns
Device tokens and identifiers
Location Data
How We Use Location Data
In-use Location
Shows nearest petrol stations and personalizes your experience
Background Location
Updates prices for nearby stations and improves service accuracy
Security Measures
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:
Data Storage
• Encrypted databases
• Secure cloud infrastructure
• Regular security audits
Transmission
• SSL/TLS encryption
• Secure API endpoints
• Protected data transfers
Data Processing Agreement
For business users and station owners:
• Compliance with GDPR and data protection laws
• Data processor obligations and responsibilities
• Sub-processor management and oversight
• Data breach notification procedures
User Generated Content
Regarding price updates and reviews:
• Users grant us license to use submitted content
• Content must be accurate and truthful
• We reserve the right to remove content
• Users are responsible for their submissions
Data Retention and Deletion
Retention Periods
• Account data: Until account deletion
• Price history: 14 months
• Usage logs: 90 days
• Backup data: 30 days
Deletion Requests
• Process for requesting data deletion
• Exceptions for legal requirements
• Verification procedures
• Timeline for completion
Automated Decision Making
Information about our automated processes:
• Price validation algorithms
• Fraud detection systems
• Account suspension procedures
• Appeal processes
Legal Protections
Indemnification
Users agree to indemnify and hold FuelCompare harmless from any claims resulting from:
• Violation of terms
• Inaccurate price submissions
• Unauthorized use
• Third-party claims
Limitation of Liability
Specific limitations on damages and legal remedies:
• Maximum liability amounts
• Excluded damages
• Force majeure events
• Service interruptions
